des:
In this busy day to day life, its very difficult to get time to fix our health issues. In this situation, we're having a great chance to get daily home remedies for our health. It provides day to day information about latest home remedies about fitness and health. 
You can invoke this skill by saying 'Alexa open daily home remedies'.
